    "**A separate tool-walk skill** \u2014 rejected: duplicates step 8.5's pull / classify / gate logic; two procedures drift; the founder-facing gate would fire from two places.",
    "**A weaker tool-EXISTS bar (handler serving is enough)** \u2014 rejected: reintroduces exactly the false-EXISTS bypass (MUC-02) the change exists to close; violates FR-09 / NFR-S02."
